          },
          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Measurement of macroscopic and microscopic thermal",
                " neutron cross sections of V,Co,In,Dy and Au using",
                " neutron self absorption properties"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "I.Celenk",
                "H.Demirel",
                "A.Ozmen"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,JRN,148,393,1991",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,JRN,148,393,1991",
                    "doi": "10.1007/BF02060371",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "JRN",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "148",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": null,
                        "page": "393"
                      },
                      "date": 1991
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Main ref."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "2TUKANR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "PU-BE"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A 5 Ci Pu238-Be neutron source immersed in a",
                "water tank was used. The thermal flux is about 1.e4",
                "n/cm2/S at the irradiation position."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Thermal neutron spectrum"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The neutron activation technique combined",
                " with a neutron self-absorption method was used.",
                " For each element, foils of different thicknesses were",
                " activated with thermal neutrons and the induced gamma-",
                " activity measured."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma activity was counted using a high",
                " purity Ge detector which has an efficiency of 12.45%",
                " relative to a 3by3 inch NaI detector, a FWHM of 2 keV",
                "  at 1332 keV and a peak to compton ration of 42."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma-photopeak areas as a function of foil",
                " thickness were model fitted to yield the total thermal",
                " neutron macroscopic cross section, from which the",
                " microscopic cross-section was calculated dividing",
                " the macroscopic cross section by the number of nuclei",
                " per cm3."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Correction for gamma-self absorption was made on the",
                " basis of experimental photopeak areas by using the",
                " linear attenuation coefficients determined using",
                " foils of different thicknesses for each element.",
                " For the V foils,no gamma-self-absorption was observed."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "STATUS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "status": [
                  "TABLE"
                ],
                "subentry_number": null,
                "author": null,
                "reference": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Tbl.5 from J.Radioanal.Nucl.Chem.,148(1991)393"
