          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The V foils were irradiated for 8 min, transferred to",
                "counting in 1 min, counted for 8 min and returned to",
                "the irradiation position in 1 min. The process was",
                "repeated 5 times- i.e. with the cyclic activation",
                "technique. All foils were irradiated with and without",
                "Cd covers and the epithermal contribution was",
                "subtracted.",
                " Thickness    Geom.form   Width/diam.   Purity",
